# Keep the monorepo build context lean (used by the repo-root Docker builds).
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/build
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/.terraform
**/*.tfstate*
.git
.github
**/*.log
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
# Frontend is excluded from the lean backend build contexts, EXCEPT auth-baalvion, which is the one
# frontend image built from the repo root (deploy-core-stack core-auth-baalvion). Re-include just it;
# its build artifacts stay excluded by the **/node_modules etc. rules below.
Frontend/*
!Frontend/auth-baalvion
Frontend/auth-baalvion/node_modules
Frontend/auth-baalvion/.next
Frontend/auth-baalvion/.turbo
e2e
docs
*.md
